OmhDesignationUse

Open mHealth ValueSet Designation Use is defined to extend the designation use concepts to representing the term used in the CodeableConcept .text element.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in http://www.fhir.org/guides/mfhir/CodeSystem/designation-use
